#𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐑𝐂𝐘𝐂𝐀𝐥𝐞𝐫𝐭: At 8:28 PM on September 13, 2025, a fire broke out in Happy Land, Brgy. 105, Tondo, Manila involving residential light materials.

🔥Positive Alarm: 8:28 PM
🚨1st and 2nd Alarm 8:31 PM
🚨3rd Alarm: 8:36 PM
🚨4th Alarm: 9:35 PM
🚨Task Force Alpha: 10:48 PM
🚨Task Force Bravo: 10:53 PM
⚠️ As of now, the fire is still ongoing and emergency response is active. 

𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐯𝐢𝐠𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐭, 𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐝𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞𝐥𝐲, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐳𝐞 𝐬𝐚𝐟𝐞𝐭𝐲.
Let’s embody the spirit of humanitarian service and unity in times of crisis. 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐢𝐧𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐧 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐭𝐨 𝐝𝐨 𝐝𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐚 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐬:
https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BShAiv5E7/

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐮𝐩𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬:
https://txtfire.net/ 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐲 𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 (𝐄𝐌𝐄𝐑𝐆𝐄𝐍𝐂𝐘 𝐇𝐎𝐓𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐄):
📞 Red Cross Philippines - 143
📞 Department of Health - 911 or 1555
📞 Bureau of Fire Protection - 911
📞 Philippine National Police (PNP) - 911 or 117
📞 Metro Manila Development Authority (MMDA) - 136

#𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐑𝐂𝐘𝐂𝐀𝐥𝐞𝐫𝐭: At 8:28 PM on September 13, 2025, a fire broke out in Happy Land, Brgy. 105, Tondo, Manila involving residential light materials.

🔥Positive Alarm: 8:28 PM
🚨1st and 2nd Alarm 8:31 PM
🚨3rd Alarm: 8:36 PM
🚨4th Alarm: 9:35 PM
🚨Task Force Alpha: 10:48 PM
🚨Task Force Bravo: 10:53 PM
⚠️ As of now, the fire is still ongoing and emergency response is active. 

𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐯𝐢𝐠𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐭, 𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐝𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞𝐥𝐲, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐳𝐞 𝐬𝐚𝐟𝐞𝐭𝐲.
Let’s embody the spirit of humanitarian service and unity in times of crisis. 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐢𝐧𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐧 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐭𝐨 𝐝𝐨 𝐝𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐚 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐬:
https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BShAiv5E7/

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐮𝐩𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬:
https://txtfire.net/ 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐲 𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 (𝐄𝐌𝐄𝐑𝐆𝐄𝐍𝐂𝐘 𝐇𝐎𝐓𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐄):
📞 Red Cross Philippines - 143
📞 Department of Health - 911 or 1555
📞 Bureau of Fire Protection - 911
📞 Philippine National Police (PNP) - 911 or 117
📞 Metro Manila Development Authority (MMDA) - 136

message.text:
#𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐑𝐂𝐘𝐂𝐀𝐥𝐞𝐫𝐭: At 8:28 PM on September 13, 2025, a fire broke out in Happy Land, Brgy. 105, Tondo, Manila involving residential light materials.

🔥Positive Alarm: 8:28 PM
🚨1st and 2nd Alarm 8:31 PM
🚨3rd Alarm: 8:36 PM
🚨4th Alarm: 9:35 PM
🚨Task Force Alpha: 10:48 PM
🚨Task Force Bravo: 10:53 PM
⚠️ As of now, the fire is still ongoing and emergency response is active. 

𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐯𝐢𝐠𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐭, 𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐝𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞𝐥𝐲, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐳𝐞 𝐬𝐚𝐟𝐞𝐭𝐲.
Let’s embody the spirit of humanitarian service and unity in times of crisis. 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐢𝐧𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐧 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐭𝐨 𝐝𝐨 𝐝𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐚 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐬:
https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BShAiv5E7/

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐮𝐩𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬:
https://txtfire.net/ 

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐲 𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 (𝐄𝐌𝐄𝐑𝐆𝐄𝐍𝐂𝐘 𝐇𝐎𝐓𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐄):
📞 Red Cross Philippines - 143
📞 Department of Health - 911 or 1555
📞 Bureau of Fire Protection - 911
📞 Philippine National Police (PNP) - 911 or 117
📞 Metro Manila Development Authority (MMDA) - 136
